{
  "texts": [
    "In stratified tenfold cross validation, accuracy varied from 0.72 to 0.78, sensitivity varied from 0.71 to 0.80, specificity varied from 0.72 to 0.76, precision varied from 0.73 to 0.78.",
    "The RF model obtained the highest accuracy, sensitivity, specificity, precision, and F1 score.",
    "The AUROC varied from 0.76 to 0.87, and the AUPRC varied from 0.75 to 0.87.",
    "The RF model obtained the highest accuracy, sensitivity, specificity, precision, F1 score, AUROC, and AUPRC.",
    "The NN with attention model provided the highest specificity."
  ]
}